<p style="margin: 0 0 16px 0; color: #111827; font-size: 15px;">
  Hi {{recipientName}},
</p>

<p style="margin: 0 0 16px 0; color: #374151; font-size: 14px;">
  A billing update has been generated for your case.
</p>

<div style="background: #f9fafb; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 6px; padding: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px;">
  <p style="margin: 0 0 8px 0;"><strong>Case Number:</strong> {{caseNumber}}</p>
  <p style="margin: 0 0 8px 0;"><strong>Case Title:</strong> {{caseTitle}}</p>
  <p style="margin: 0 0 8px 0;"><strong>Bill Type:</strong> {{billType}}</p>
  <p style="margin: 0 0 8px 0;"><strong>Amount:</strong> {{currency}} {{amount}}</p>
  <p style="margin: 0;"><strong>Due Date:</strong> {{dueDate}}</p>
</div>

<p style="margin: 0; color: #374151; font-size: 14px;">
  <strong>Description:</strong> {{description}}
</p>
